We are Family Medical Practice - the largest and oldest foreign, privately-owned, international health care provider in Vietnam. With 6 clinics in major cities within Vietnam, FMP delivers personalized support, customer service, and comprehensive medical care for the best value to our foreign and local populations. Our multinational team of physicians comes from the US, Canada, Israel, France, Belgium, Italy, Switzerland, the UK, Japan, Philippines, Australia, Vietnam and Argentina. We are a growing and thriving company.

